Peanutbutter_Products.disclaimer: This list includes food subject to recall in the United States since March 2009 related to pistachios distributed by Setton Pistachio of Terra Bella, Inc. This list will be updated as new information is received. The information is current as of the date indicated. Once included, all food recalls will remain listed. If we learn that any information is not accurate, we will revise the list as soon as possible. When available, this database also includes photos of recalled food products that have been voluntarily submitted by recalling firms to the FDA to assist the public in identifying those products that are subject to recall.
